data.description: Very spacious open floor plan with 2 large Family Rooms, renovations were done to include Air/Heat, Doors, Windows, Wood Laminate Floors (No Carpet), Granite in Kitchen and Baths, Cabinets, Appliances (some not yet used), Electrical Wiring, Plumbing and so much more.  Refrigerator and Washer/Dryer to remain.  Large, fenced back yard. Move in Ready home with plenty of room. No HOA fees.
